LSE Agrees to Sell Servizio Titoli to Computershare

-- B y   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 
2011-04-05T06:15:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-05/lse-agrees-to-sell-servizio-titoli-to-computershare-correct-.html
(Corrects Computershare name in headline.)  London Stock Exchange Group Plc (LSE) 
agreed to sell Servizio Titoli SpA, a provider of shareholder
management services to listed companies in Italy, to
 Computershare Ltd. (CPU)  for 30 million euros ($43 million) plus an
amount of up to 2.4 million euros for the net cash balance as at
completion.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Rummer at 
 arummer@bloomberg.net  